function is a single unit, inside the function we wrote the logic/functionality.
when we need same kind of functionality we will call this function name.

syntax:-

def function_name(parameter):
    statement/logic/functionality
    return data

function_name(arguments)


type of function:-

2 types

inbuilt function
user define function


